<div
  style='position: absolute; inset: 0; padding: 18px; font-family: "Geist", sans-serif; font-size: 11px; color: #3a3a3a; overflow: hidden;'
>
  <svg
    viewBox="0 0 360 200"
    width="100%"
    height="100%"
    preserveAspectRatio="none"
    style="position: absolute; inset: 0;"
  >
    <line x1="180" y1="60" x2="120" y2="95" stroke="#9a9a9a" stroke-width="1"
    ></line>
    <line x1="180" y1="60" x2="180" y2="120" stroke="#9a9a9a" stroke-width="1"
    ></line>
    <line x1="180" y1="60" x2="240" y2="100" stroke="#9a9a9a" stroke-width="1"
    ></line>
    <line x1="180" y1="60" x2="160" y2="155" stroke="#9a9a9a" stroke-width="1"
    ></line>
    <circle cx="180" cy="60" r="4" fill="#2a2a2a"></circle>
    <circle cx="120" cy="95" r="3.5" fill="#2a2a2a"></circle>
    <circle cx="240" cy="100" r="3.5" fill="#2a2a2a"></circle>
    <circle cx="180" cy="120" r="3.5" fill="#2a2a2a"></circle>
    <circle cx="160" cy="155" r="3.5" fill="#2a2a2a"></circle>
  </svg>

  <div
    style='position: absolute; left: 22px; top: 78px; font-family: Georgia, serif; font-style: italic; font-size: 44px; color: #2a2a2a; letter-spacing: -0.01em; pointer-events: none;'
  >
    Inknote
  </div>

  <div
    style="position: absolute; left: 168px; top: 110px; width: 132px; background: #f9f7f0; border: 1px solid #cfcfcb; border-radius: 3px; padding: 5px 7px; box-shadow: 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,.04);"
  >
    <div
      style='display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; font-style: italic; font-family: Georgia, serif; font-size: 9.5px; color: #3a3a3a;'
    >
      <span>Be specific about context</span>
      <span style="color: #999;">×</span>
    </div>
    <div style="height: 1px; background: #dcdcd8; margin: 4px 0;"></div>
    <div
      style='font-family: Georgia, serif; font-size: 8.5px; line-height: 1.35; color: #3a3a3a;'
    >
      Always provide relevant background information. Is this a greenfield
      project?
    </div>
  </div>

  <div
    style='position: absolute; left: 250px; top: 70px; width: 110px; background: #f9f7f0; border: 1px solid #cfcfcb; border-radius: 3px; padding: 5px 7px;'
  >
    <div
      style='font-style: italic; font-family: Georgia, serif; font-size: 9.5px; color: #3a3a3a; border-bottom: 1px solid #dcdcd8; padding-bottom: 3px; margin-bottom: 3px;'
    >
      Algorithm analysis
    </div>
    <div
      style='font-family: Georgia, serif; font-size: 8px; line-height: 1.35; color: #3a3a3a;'
    >
      Performance involves analyzing time and space complexity using big-O
      notation.
    </div>
  </div>

  <div
    style="position: absolute; left: 215px; top: 125px; width: 0; height: 0; border-style: solid; border-width: 0 0 10px 7px; border-color: transparent transparent #ea833e transparent; transform: rotate(-15deg); opacity: .85;"
  >
  </div>
</div>
